Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 1 June 2025
Welcome to Ting Xie App. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our iOS educational App.
By using our App, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:
a. Personal Information
Email address and password used for account registration and login (via Firebase Authentication).

b. Usage & Device Data
We collect usage data to help improve the app and user experience. This may include:
Activity within the app (e.g., lessons/questions attempted, scores, session start/end times).
App interaction events such as sign-ins, sign-outs, and crash logs.
Country or region based on device location settings or IP address.
Device information, such as device model and operating system version.

This data is collected automatically through Firebase Analytics and Firestore.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
Authenticate and manage your account.
Store and analyze learning progress.
Understand how users interact with the App across different regions and devices.
Improve App performance, fix technical issues, and enhance user experience.
Provide customer support and manage your subscription status.

3. Subscriptions & Payments
Our app includes auto-renewing subscriptions managed via the Apple App Store.
We do not collect or store your payment information.
All subscription billing and management is handled securely by Apple.
You can manage your subscription in your Apple ID account settings.

4. Data Sharing
We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data:
With Firebase (a Google service) for authentication, analytics, and data storage.
With service providers as necessary to support our operations.
As required by law, such as to comply with legal obligations or requests from authorities.

5. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your data, including:
Use of Firebase’s secure infrastructure.
Encrypted connections (HTTPS) and secure storage. However, no system is completely secure. We cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.

6. Your Rights and Choices
You can:
View and update your account information in the App.
Request deletion of your account and associated data by contacting us.
Limit data collection by adjusting your device’s privacy settings.

To make any data-related requests, contact us at tingxie2025@gmail.com.

7. Children’s Privacy
Our app is designed for children to use under the supervision of a parent, guardian, or educator. We do not knowingly collect personal data directly from children under 13 without verified parental consent.

8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make changes, we will update the "Effective Date" above and may notify users via email or in-App messaging.

9. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about this policy, please contact:
Email: tingxieapp2025@gmail.com
App Name: Ting Xie App

